channel.title: Need Server Coder - Good deal
channel.description:
Hi, I'm currently looking for a server coder. So I can move along faster in my project. I'm currently looking for someone that is well experienced and can code pretty well. At the end of the project you can get $50.00 USD - $100.00 USD In pay pal, western union, or the mail(Not a good choice with the mail) You will also get 50% profits I actually make from the server. By selling Administrator for a range of 5.00 - 10.00 USD. Yes, a lot of my friends do buy Administrator so each time they buy it for 10 dollars you get 5 dollars in the mail But you have to be on a lot if I need you and you have to actually fix/do what I say when I need it. If something comes up family wise I don't really care because family is family and you can't be on if somethings wrong. The $50.00 - $100.00 USD depends on how well you code and how much you actually do for me.
NOTE: If this Project turns out better then I thought you can get over $100.00. Do you know why I would pay that much? Mostly because I love to have the best of things, I'm sorry but that's the way I like it but it will never happen. There will always be something/someone better.
Thanks, Justin
